						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Sati stone on the tank bund.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records the death by <hi rend="italic">Sahagamana</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Chimmyi,</hi> wife a <hi rend="italic">Harikāra</hi> (name lost) in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Bhva, Jyēshṭha ba. 9, [Tuesday].</hi> The Śaka year is not given. The characters belong to the <hi rend="bold">14th century A.D.</hi></p>						

